15/* RFC3658 */
16
17#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_DLV_32769_C
18#define RDATA_GENERIC_DLV_32769_C
19
20#define RRTYPE_DLV_ATTRIBUTES 0
21
22#include <dns/ds.h>
23
24static inline isc_result_t
25fromtext_dlv(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
26
27 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
28
29 return (generic_fromtext_ds(rdclass, type, lexer, origin, options,
30 target, callbacks));
31}
32
33static inline isc_result_t
34totext_dlv(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
35
36 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
37
38 return (generic_totext_ds(rdata, tctx, target));
39}
40
41static inline isc_result_t
42fromwire_dlv(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
43
44 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
45
46 return (generic_fromwire_ds(rdclass, type, source, dctx, options,
47 target));
48}
49
50static inline isc_result_t
51towire_dlv(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
52 isc_region_t sr;
53
54 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
55 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
56
57 UNUSED(cctx);
58
59 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
60 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
61}
62
63static inline int
64compare_dlv(ARGS_COMPARE) {
65 isc_region_t r1;
66 isc_region_t r2;
67
68 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
69 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
70 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
71 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
72 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
73
74 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
75 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
76 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
77}
78
79static inline isc_result_t
80fromstruct_dlv(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
81
82 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
83
84 return (generic_fromstruct_ds(rdclass, type, source, target));
85}
86
87static inline isc_result_t
88tostruct_dlv(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
89 dns_rdata_dlv_t *dlv = target;
90
91 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
92
93 dlv->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
94 dlv->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
95 ISC_LINK_INIT(&dlv->common, link);
96
97 return (generic_tostruct_ds(rdata, target, mctx));
98}
99
100static inline void
101freestruct_dlv(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
102 dns_rdata_dlv_t *dlv = source;
103
104 REQUIRE(dlv != NULL);
105 REQUIRE(dlv->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
106
107 if (dlv->mctx == NULL)
108 return;
109
110 if (dlv->digest != NULL)
111 isc_mem_free(dlv->mctx, dlv->digest);
112 dlv->mctx = NULL;
113}
114
115static inline isc_result_t
116additionaldata_dlv(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
117 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
118
119 UNUSED(rdata);
120 UNUSED(add);
121 UNUSED(arg);
122
123 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
124}
125
126static inline isc_result_t
127digest_dlv(ARGS_DIGEST) {
128 isc_region_t r;
129
130 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
131
132 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
133
134 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
135}
136
137static inline bool
138checkowner_dlv(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
139
140 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
141
142 UNUSED(name);
143 UNUSED(type);
144 UNUSED(rdclass);
145 UNUSED(wildcard);
146
147 return (true);
148}
149
150static inline bool
151checknames_dlv(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
152
153 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dlv);
154
155 UNUSED(rdata);
156 UNUSED(owner);
157 UNUSED(bad);
158
159 return (true);
160}
161
162static inline int
163casecompare_dlv(ARGS_COMPARE) {
164 return (compare_dlv(rdata1, rdata2));
165}
166
167#endif /* RDATA_GENERIC_DLV_32769_C */
